text: Marie-Eve Gahié (born 27 November 1996) is a French judoka.IJF profile She is the 2017 European bronze medalist and the 2019 World champion in the 70 kg division. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:French female judoka Category:Sportspeople from Paris Category:World judo champions Category:European Games competitors for France Category:Judoka at the 2015 European Games Category:Judoka at the 2019 European Games Category:European Games gold medalists for France Category:European Games bronze medalists for France Category:European Games medalists in judo
